    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865960/extras/059a268846b36a47b0c70f794755cf67.poster.avif?t=1765974616\" width=620 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865960/extras/059a268846b36a47b0c70f794755cf67.webm?t=1765974616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865960/extras/059a268846b36a47b0c70f794755cf67.mp4?t=1765974616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在天籁之国，音乐是生命和能量的源泉。但是自从缔造者和他们的管弦乐团消失之后，王国四分五裂，世界也慢慢沉寂了下来。能不能重新组建一支管弦乐团呢？这个问题，就要由天籁之国的神秘音乐家——飞乐梦来回答了。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865960/extras/8303f6d5e575476adebe7cd38c257ee1.avif?t=1765974616\" width=620 height=191 /></span><br><br>在你的手中，小提琴和琴弓既能演奏出天籁之音，也能助你上下翻飞。不断弹射，勇往直前，完成刺激的平台跳跃挑战，通过一个又一个关卡，同时重启王国的机械，把生命和能量带回这个世界。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865960/extras/b68314cf1744534426e489185afc6fb8.avif?t=1765974616\" width=620 height=191 /></span><br><br>天籁之国的每个区域都有截然不同的氛围和角色，每个场景都由手工绘制完成。来结识这里的音乐奇才，并说服他们加入乐团吧。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865960/extras/2e2abb31407c0e3bbe74e3633467feb8.avif?t=1765974616\" width=620 height=191 /></span><br><br>欣赏 Scoring Orchestra Paris 演奏的配乐。该配乐专为《Symphonia》录制，并由 Olivier Esman 及其团队作曲。举办引人入胜的音乐会，每场音乐会都以一类乐器为中心——弦乐器、铜管乐器以及木管乐器。<br> <br><strong>探索，追寻，演奏小提琴，聚集音乐家。唤醒天籁之国。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865960/extras/fdf70e03bd5cdfc4014a80840e0f8096.avif?t=1765974616\" width=620 height=191 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>利用飞乐梦的所有能力，体验并通过困难重重的平台跳跃挑战<br></li><li>探索结合了音乐与机械的不同场景<br></li><li>演奏小提琴，激活关卡元素，把生机带回王国<br></li><li>聚集音乐奇才，举办激动人心的音乐会，让音乐、快乐与荣耀重回这个世界</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865960/extras/b559d9380ff55a5b274c7e122bbfb376.poster.avif?t=1765974616\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865960/extras/b559d9380ff55a5b274c7e122bbfb376.webm?t=1765974616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1865960/extras/b559d9380ff55a5b274c7e122bbfb376.mp4?t=1765974616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
